| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-0304 — Recovery Inhibition (everest)"
| comment "Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 243dbf15-1cf3-56a0-b1ab-02d9c373e9df"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
